174 (a) Any person who by means of a false statement, failure to disclose information, or
175 impersonation, or by other fraudulent device, obtains, attempts to obtain, or retains for
176 himself, herself, or any other person any medical assistance or other benefit or payment
177 under this article to which such person is not entitled or in an amount greater than that to
